    "title": "ファンレター",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "届いたファンレターを\r\nグラスワンダーに手渡した。",
            "enText": "She handed the fan letter she \nreceived to Grass Wonder.",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 61,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 72,
                    "pathId": 2116481921808905617
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 72,
                    "pathId": -1563633696122672461
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3293568423914030158,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "グラスワンダー",
            "enName": "Grass Wonder",
            "jpText": "あら、この方は……\r\nまたお手紙を書いてくださったんですね。",
            "enText": "Oh, she wrote to…… again, didn't she?",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 64,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 76,
                    "pathId": 8380918324420990397
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 97,
                    "pathId": 6032138191476029570
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 99,
                    "pathId": -6267990019900643449
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4065518419568361995,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "グラスワンダー",
            "enName": "Grass Wonder",
            "jpText": "いつも通り、拝啓から始まり、\r\n敬具で締められています、ふふ……。",
            "enText": "As usual, it begins with \"Dear Sir or Madam,\" \nand ends with \"Sincerely yours.\" ……",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 66,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "気になるファンレターでも？",
                    "enText": "Even a fan letter you're curious about?",
                    "nextBlock": 4
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 99,
                    "pathId": 8150194903061282132
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 137,
                    "pathId": 1757795710278220925
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 77,
                    "pathId": 7162798091083349299
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2210996181160075054,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "グラスワンダー",
            "enName": "Grass Wonder",
            "jpText": "はい、ファンレターとしては形式ばって\r\nいますが、とても心に残るお手紙なんです。",
            "enText": "Yes, it is a formal fan letter, but it is a \nvery memorable letter.",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 71,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 101,
                    "pathId": -2284429601198194478
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 102,
                    "pathId": -6443369191730249836
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 82,
                    "pathId": -169675985227481841
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6570760859972339089,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "グラスワンダー",
            "enName": "Grass Wonder",
            "jpText": "達筆で丁寧に書かれた文字は\r\n日に日に上達していき……。",
            "enText": "The calligraphy, carefully written with a \nmasterful pen, improves day by day. ……",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "origClipLength": 63,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -9091657217095466306
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 102,
                    "pathId": 2741424656272117980
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 74,
                    "pathId": -1217682512761099226
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4922851768208449164,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "グラスワンダー",
            "enName": "Grass Wonder",
            "jpText": "それには飽き足らず、最近では季語を\r\n織り交ぜたり、一句詠まれたりも。",
            "enText": "Not content with this, she has recently been \nmixing in seasonal words and even composing a \nsingle phrase.",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "origClipLength": 67,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 71,
                    "pathId": 5622478095929414249
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 190,
                    "pathId": 4753170810380091581
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 78,
                    "pathId": -3947656878664570702
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5245321905459373517,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "グラスワンダー",
            "enName": "Grass Wonder",
            "jpText": "私の趣味嗜好をご存じの上で、\r\n一筆一筆、したためてくださったのでしょう。",
            "enText": "She must have known my tastes and wrote each \nand every stroke of my pen.",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "origClipLength": 69,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -5180826285921380296
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 190,
                    "pathId": -2332213941223426976
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 80,
                    "pathId": -3067051667389250034
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 9193247512013069933,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "グラスワンダー",
            "enName": "Grass Wonder",
            "jpText": "じんと胸の奥が温かくなってきます……。",
            "enText": "It warms my heart and chest. ……",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "origClipLength": 57,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 190,
                    "pathId": -1928595201467949356
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 68,
                    "pathId": -4434252627811993106
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1687863631681095713,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "ファンのグラスワンダーに喜んで\r\n欲しいという気持ちが、自分にも\n伝わってくるようだ。",
            "enText": "It seems that the fans' desire to make Grass \nWonder happy is being conveyed to me as well.",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "origClipLength": 73,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 84,
                    "pathId": 6066203451255657491
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 84,
                    "pathId": 7340688755017580417
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 601227027962286344,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "グラスワンダー",
            "enName": "Grass Wonder",
            "jpText": "この方だけでなく、日本の文化や\r\n地域の風習を紹介してくれる方も……。",
            "enText": "This is not the only person who can introduce \nyou to Japanese culture and local customs. ……",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "origClipLength": 102,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 93,
                    "pathId": -5028110034877076215
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 217,
                    "pathId": -6836680757848505904
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5565643794796097323,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "グラスワンダー",
            "enName": "Grass Wonder",
            "jpText": "全国からたくさん届く、このような手紙を\r\n受け取る度に私は――",
            "enText": "Every time I receive one of these \nletters, of which I receive many \nfrom all over the country, I―",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "origClipLength": 65,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "頑張りたくなるね",
                    "enText": "Makes you want to work harder.",
                    "nextBlock": 12
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 71,
                    "pathId": -4988022160463748104
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 76,
                    "pathId": 184508328497252206
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 76,
                    "pathId": -4547341037487915537
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -603784409484692708,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "グラスワンダー",
            "enName": "Grass Wonder",
            "jpText": "ええ、そうですね～。\r\nより一層、負けられなくなるんです――",
            "enText": "Yes, I know! It makes it even more unbeatable―",
            "nextBlock": 13,
            "origClipLength": 64,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -5188853912795098190
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 40,
                    "pathId": -5834848100564487012
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 75,
                    "pathId": 1391836099284429622
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4934476076027160747,
            "blockIdx": 12
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "グラスワンダーの瞳に\r\n静かな闘志が灯る。",
            "enText": "A quiet fighting spirit lights up in the eyes \nof Grass Wonder.",
            "nextBlock": 14,
            "origClipLength": 58,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 69,
                    "pathId": 1744380259810428465
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 69,
                    "pathId": -7441901211588359884
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5392104003298894307,
            "blockIdx": 13
        },
        {
            "jpName": "グラスワンダー",
            "enName": "Grass Wonder",
            "jpText": "水火も辞せず尽力して参りますので、\r\n今後もよろしくお願いいたしますね。",
            "enText": "I will continue to make every \neffort to work with you.",
            "nextBlock": 15,
            "origClipLength": 68,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 25,
                    "pathId": 8345604535378304526
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 79,
                    "pathId": -3139987251486330901
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1032019019465482342,
            "blockIdx": 14
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "ファンからの応援で、グラスワンダーの\r\nやる気も上がったようだ。",
            "enText": "The support from her fans seemed \nto motivate Grass Wonder.",
            "nextBlock": -1,
            "origClipLength": 65,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 76,
                    "pathId": 1329578713996895603
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 76,
                    "pathId": -9008430586501332469
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 9076164218688222650,
            "blockIdx": 15
        }
